<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      /* Ensure images scale properly */
      img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      /* Text overlay on image */
      .image-container {
        position: relative;
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .overlay-text {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      .content {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='content'>
      <h1 style='font-weight:bold;'>Hey {{firstName}}!</h1>

      <h3 style='margin-top:60px;'>
        We noticed you haven’t followed up after applying to work with
        <strong>LaceyStrong Coaching</strong>
        — and we get it. Life gets busy. But if you’re still thinking about
        chasing that next level in your training, now’s the time to move.
      </h3>

      <h3>
        <strong>Coach Lacey Pruitt</strong>
        has a limited number of openings left this month, and because you
        applied, we’re offering you an
        <strong>exclusive 50% OFF your 1st month</strong>
        of coaching to lock in your spot.
      </h3>

      <h3>
        This isn’t just another cookie-cutter program. Lacey has coached
        athletes to 49 overall wins, earned 5x Coach of the Year, and brings
        elite-level experience to every client — whether you’re prepping for the
        stage or leveling up your lifestyle.
      </h3>
    </div>

    <div class='image-container'>
      <img
        src='https://lacey-strong.onrender.com/images/no-reply-img.png'
        alt='Coaching image'
      />
      <div class='overlay-text'>
        If you're serious, reply to this email and we’ll get your setup started.<br
        />
        <strong>Chase Your Why.</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>